trans-unit.source: Visual Studio Mac Licensing and Purchase on to use existing Visual Studio license on a Mac.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio Mac Licensing and Purchase on to use existing Visual Studio license on a Mac.

trans-unit.source: Can I use my existing Visual Studio license on a Mac?
trans-unit.target: Can I use my existing Visual Studio license on a Mac?

trans-unit.source: If you have purchased a Visual Studio Professional or Enterprise Subscription (Standard or Cloud), the license applies to Visual Studio for Mac as well.
trans-unit.target: If you have purchased a Visual Studio Professional or Enterprise Subscription (Standard or Cloud), the license applies to Visual Studio for Mac as well.

trans-unit.source: Standalone Licenses for Visual Studio Professional 2019 do not apply to Visual Studio for Mac.
trans-unit.target: Standalone Licenses for Visual Studio Professional 2019 do not apply to Visual Studio for Mac.

trans-unit.source: For more information, please refer to the subscription documentation.
trans-unit.target: For more information, please refer to the subscription documentation.
